timest = time.time()
assert Chronyk(timest) > Chronyk(timest - 5)
assert Chronyk(timest, timezone=0) > timest - 5
assert Chronyk(timest) < Chronyk(timest + 5)
assert Chronyk(timest, timezone=0) < timest + 5
assert Chronyk(timest) <= Chronyk(timest)
assert Chronyk(timest, timezone=0) <= timest
assert Chronyk(timest) >= Chronyk(timest - 5)
assert Chronyk(timest, timezone=0) >= timest - 5
